essible higher topological complexity\neven when the regular topological complexity is not so accessible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 19:30:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2015 16:31:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-19"}
