nansatz. The resulting inelastic CT14QED PDFs will be made available to the\npublic. In addition, we also provide CT14QEDinc PDFs, in which the {\\em\ninclusive} photon PDF at the scale $Q_0$ is defined by the sum of the inelastic\nphoton PDF and the elastic photon distribution obtained from the Equivalent\nPhoton Approximation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 19:53:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2016 19:53:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
